    "causal_summary": "The hardened J1 to J4 generators ship their idempotent content-hashed writes, enum-clean derived status, prefixed paths and preserved parent links behind default-OFF flags, so the existing repo still carries the legacy format the new contract rejects. This Stage 3 migration regenerates every description.json and graph-metadata.json across the whole repo including z_archive and z_future onto the new format, driven by the scoped per-folder generator looped over every folder rather than the legacy over-reaching tree-walk. It is gated on a byte-stable second run that yields no diff, zero enum, parent_id and path violations under the phase 036 validator, and a validate-clean tree, and it lands as scoped commits batched by track. The phase is HARD-GATED on phases 033 through 036 being done and tested.",
